  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this platformer, you control a piece of tofu named Hamachi, who unexpectedly falls into the clutches of Demon Queen Deity, an evil fiend who intends to use him as a vessel to conquer the world through mass murder.<i></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the villain: Choose to kill, spare, or ignore every civilian.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three distinct routes: Pacifist, Neutral, and Genocide, each with its own ending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat or pacify demonic bosses, pacified bosses will join your side.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through 8 visually distinct worlds built with original pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chainsaw power-up grants temporary invincibility and destroys any being you touch.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect souls from dead civilians or sushi dropped by Penelope Pom Pom Pink to restore health.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your crimes will not go unnoticed by the authorities.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this platformer, you control a piece of tofu named Hamachi, who unexpectedly falls into the clutches of Demon Queen Deity, an evil fiend who intends to use him as a vessel to conquer the world through mass murder.<i></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the villain: Choose to kill, spare, or ignore every civilian.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three distinct routes: Pacifist, Neutral, and Genocide, each with its own ending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat or pacify demonic bosses, pacified bosses will join your side.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through 8 visually distinct worlds built with original pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chainsaw power-up grants temporary invincibility and destroys any being you touch.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect souls from dead civilians or sushi dropped by Penelope Pom Pom Pink to restore health.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your crimes will not go unnoticed by the authorities.</p></li></ul>",
